001
002package com.commercetools.api.models.cart;
003
004import com.commercetools.api.models.Referencable;
005import com.commercetools.api.models.ResourceIdentifiable;
006
007public interface CartMixin extends Referencable<Cart>, ResourceIdentifiable<Cart> {
008    @Override
009    default CartResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier() {
010        return CartResourceIdentifier.builder().id(getId()).build();
011    }
012
013    @Override
014    default CartReference toReference() {
015        return CartReference.builder().id(getId()).build();
016    }
017
018}
